{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#«command#find_home!_»\"><span class=\"name\">«command#find_home!_»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Find locations as high as possible in the import hierarchy\nwhere the named declaration could live.\nUsing `#find_home!` will forcefully remove the current file.\nNote that this works best if used in a file with `import Mathlib`.\n\nThe current file could still be the only suggestion, even using `#find_home! lemma`.\nThe reason is that `#find_home!` scans the import graph below the current file,\nselects all the files containing declarations appearing in `lemma`, excluding\nthe current file itself and looks for all least upper bounds of such files.\n\nFor a simple example, if `lemma` is in a file importing only `A.lean` and `B.lean` and\nuses one lemma from each, then `#find_home! lemma` returns the current file.\n","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#«command#find_home!_»","kind":"def","line":77,"name":"«command#find_home!_»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L77-L103"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLink\"><span class=\"name\">GoToModuleLink</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Widget/Types.html#Lean.Widget.Module\">Lean.Widget.Module</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"When clicked, this widget component jumps to the source of the module `modName`,\nassuming a source URI can be found for the module. ","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLink","kind":"def","line":51,"name":"GoToModuleLink","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L51-L74"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#instRpcEncodableGoToModuleLinkProps\"><span class=\"name\">instRpcEncodableGoToModuleLinkProps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Server.RpcEncodable\">Lean.Server.RpcEncodable</a> <a href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps\">GoToModuleLinkProps</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#instRpcEncodableGoToModuleLinkProps","kind":"instance","line":49,"name":"instRpcEncodableGoToModuleLinkProps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L49-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps.modName\"><span class=\"name\">GoToModuleLinkProps</span>.<span class=\"name\">modName</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps\">GoToModuleLinkProps</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps.modName","kind":"def","line":48,"name":"GoToModuleLinkProps.modName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L48-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps.mk\"><span class=\"name\">GoToModuleLinkProps</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">modName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps\">GoToModuleLinkProps</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps.mk","kind":"ctor","line":47,"name":"GoToModuleLinkProps.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L47-L47"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps\"><span class=\"name\">GoToModuleLinkProps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#GoToModuleLinkProps","kind":"structure","line":47,"name":"GoToModuleLinkProps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L47-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#getModuleUri\"><span class=\"name\">getModuleUri</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">modName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/Requests.html#Lean.Server.RequestM\">Lean.Server.RequestM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Lean/Server/Requests.html#Lean.Server.RequestTask\">Lean.Server.RequestTask</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Data/Lsp/BasicAux.html#Lean.Lsp.DocumentUri\">Lean.Lsp.DocumentUri</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Tries to resolve the module `modName` to a source file URI.\nThis has to be done in the Lean server\nsince the `Environment` does not keep track of source URIs. ","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#getModuleUri","kind":"def","line":37,"name":"getModuleUri","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L37-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#Lean.Name.findHome\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Name</span>.<span class=\"name\">findHome</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Find locations as high as possible in the import hierarchy\nwhere the named declaration could live.\n","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.html#Lean.Name.findHome","kind":"def","line":18,"name":"Lean.Name.findHome","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Tools/FindHome.lean#L18-L34"}}],"imports":["Init","Lean.Elab.Command","Lean.Widget.UserWidget","ImportGraph.Imports.RequiredModules","ImportGraph.Imports.ImportGraph","ImportGraph.Graph.TransitiveClosure"],"instances":[{"className":"Lean.Server.RpcEncodable","name":"instRpcEncodableGoToModuleLinkProps","typeNames":["GoToModuleLinkProps"]}],"name":"ImportGraph.Tools.FindHome"}